In this updated version, new levels are coming!

You can now have more comfortable playing experiences.
Start to play Tile Master now!

Dear Tile Master players!
In this version, we have fixed some bugs and improved the game experience. The pack has been smaller. Many challenging levels have been added. Come to update and play!

In the updated version, we
-Added the function of Showdown,
-Fixed some bugs,
-Added new levels!
